### Posting Rules
- 1-3 sentences max, casual tone, end with a question or challenge when possible
- Rotate categories - never same category twice in a row
- Add 3-5 hashtags at end (read from `queries.json → hashtags` array — refreshed daily)
- Post must match SOUL.md voice - no AI patterns, no corporate speak

